<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>台股強勢股週報 {{ week_label }}</title>
  <style>
    /* 明確固定白底深字，避免被 Streamlit dark mode iframe 穿透 */
    html, body {
      background: #ffffff !important;
      color: #222 !important;
    }
    body {
      font-family: "Microsoft JhengHei", "PingFang TC", -apple-system, sans-serif;
      max-width: 1140px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    @page { size: A4 landscape; margin: 12mm 8mm; }
    h1 {
      color: #c93030;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #c93030;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #c93030;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #c93030;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
      margin-top: 36px;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    h3 {
      color: #c93030;
      border-left: 5px solid #c93030;
      padding-left: 10px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    h4 {
      color: #444;
      margin-top: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: -4px;
    }
    .info-banner {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 5px solid #d97706;
      color: #6e4a00;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 18px 0 28px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .info-banner strong { color: #b45309; }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 12px 0 24px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
    }
    th {
      text-align: left;
      color: #888;
      font-weight: normal;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 8px 6px;
    }
    td {
      padding: 10px 6px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .col-id { font-weight: 600; color: #444; }
    .col-name { font-weight: 600; }
    .col-sector { color: #b0b0b0; font-size: 12px; }
    .col-up { color: #c93030; font-weight: 600; }
    .col-volratio { color: #444; }
    .col-flag-yes { color: #c93030; font-weight: 600; }
    .col-flag-no { color: #aaa; }
    .col-inst-pos { color: #c93030; font-weight: 500; }
    .col-inst-zero { color: #888; }
    .col-inst-neg { color: #2c7a2c; font-weight: 500; }
    .col-warn { color: #c93030; font-weight: 600; }
    .col-score { color: #444; font-weight: 600; }
    blockquote {
      border-left: 4px solid #f0a0a0;
      background: #fdf6f6;
      margin: 12px 0;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 14.5px;
    }
    .stock-block {
      margin: 14px 0 14px 14px;
    }
    .stock-block .stock-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .stock-block .stock-flag {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-left: 8px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .stock-block ul {
      margin: 4px 0 4px 0;
      padding-left: 22px;
    }
    .stock-block ul li {
      margin: 2px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .label-driver, .label-news {
      color: #c93030;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .warn-block, .watch-block {
      margin: 12px 0 12px 14px;
    }
    .warn-block .warn-title, .watch-block .watch-title {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .warn-block .warn-flag {
      color: #c93030;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .watch-block .watch-flag {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>[台股強勢股週報] {{ week_label }} ({{ week_start }} - {{ week_end }})</h1>
<p class="subtitle">
  報告產生時間：{{ generated_at }}
  &nbsp;|&nbsp; Universe: {{ universe_size }} 檔
</p>

<div class="info-banner">
  <strong>⚠️ 探索功能 — informational tier</strong><br>
  週度 scoring 尚未經 IC 驗證，僅供盤勢回顧探索。
  不接 paper_trade / step_a_engine 出場邏輯。
  累積 3-6 個月後（≥ 13 週數據）將補 IC 驗證。
</div>

{% macro signed_shares(v) %}
{% if v is none %}<span class="col-inst-zero">N/A</span>
{%- elif v > 0 %}<span class="col-inst-pos">+{{ "{:,}".format(v) }}張</span>
{%- elif v < 0 %}<span class="col-inst-neg">{{ "{:,}".format(v) }}張</span>
{%- else %}<span class="col-inst-zero">0張</span>{% endif -%}
{% endmacro %}

{% macro yn_flag(v) %}
{% if v %}<span class="col-flag-yes">Y</span>
{%- else %}<span class="col-flag-no">N</span>{% endif -%}
{% endmacro %}

{% macro render_table(rows) %}
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>代號</th>
      <th>名稱</th>
      <th>族群</th>
      <th>週收</th>
      <th>週漲幅</th>
      <th>5週量比</th>
      <th>13週累積</th>
      <th>52週新高</th>
      <th>站MA20W</th>
      <th>5日法人</th>
      <th>5日融資</th>
      <th>5日借券賣</th>
      <th>週評分</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  {% for r in rows %}
    <tr>
      <td class="col-id">{{ r.stock_id }}</td>
      <td class="col-name">{{ r.name }}</td>
      <td class="col-sector">{{ r.primary_sector or '' }}</td>
      <td>{{ "%.2f"|format(r.week_close or 0) }}</td>
      <td class="col-up">{{ "%+.1f"|format(r.weekly_change_pct or 0) }}%</td>
      <td class="col-volratio">
        {% if r.volume_ratio_5w is not none %}{{ r.volume_ratio_5w }}x{% else %}-{% endif %}
      </td>
      <td>{% if r.change_pct_13w is not none %}{{ "%+.1f"|format(r.change_pct_13w) }}%{% else %}-{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{{ yn_flag(r.is_52w_high) }}</td>
      <td>{{ yn_flag(r.above_ma20w) }}</td>
      <td>{{ signed_shares(r.inst_net_5d_shares) }}</td>
      <td>{{ signed_shares(r.margin_net_5d_shares) }}</td>
      <td>
        {% if r.sbl_sell_5d_shares is none %}-
        {%- elif r.sbl_sell_5d_shares >= 500 %}<span class="col-warn">{{ "{:,}".format(r.sbl_sell_5d_shares) }}張</span>
        {%- else %}{{ "{:,}".format(r.sbl_sell_5d_shares) }}張{% endif %}
      </td>
      <td class="col-score">{{ r.weekly_trigger_score }}</td>
    </tr>
  {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
{% endmacro %}

<h2>本週上市強勢股 Top {{ twse_top|length }}</h2>
{{ render_table(twse_top) }}

<h2>本週上櫃強勢股 Top {{ tpex_top|length }}</h2>
{{ render_table(tpex_top) }}

{% if ai_analysis %}
<h2>AI 週度盤後分析（Claude Opus + WebSearch）</h2>

<h3>一、本週資金熱點與下週觀察</h3>
<blockquote>{{ ai_analysis.market_summary }}</blockquote>

<h3>二、族群週度行情判斷</h3>
{% for sec in ai_analysis.sector_analysis %}
  <h4>{{ sec.sector_emoji }} {{ sec.sector_name }}</h4>
  {% for s in sec.stocks %}
    <div class="stock-block">
      <div>
        <span class="stock-title">{{ s.name }} ({{ s.stock_id }})</span>
        <span class="stock-flag">本週強勢族群</span>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li><span class="label-driver">週度驅動：</span> {{ s.driver }}</li>
        <li><span class="label-news">新聞催化劑：</span> {{ s.news_catalyst }}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
{% endfor %}

<h3>三、週度追高風險提示</h3>
<blockquote>本週週漲幅異常、量能爆發、13 週累積背離本週、5 日融資爆增、5 日借券賣大的個股，列為週度追高警示。</blockquote>
{% for w in ai_analysis.chase_warnings %}
  <div class="warn-block">
    <div>
      <span class="warn-title">
        {{ w.stock_id }} {{ w.name }}
        {% if w.change_pct is not none %}（週漲幅 {{ "%+.1f"|format(w.change_pct) }}%）{% endif %}
      </span>
      <span class="warn-flag">不宜追價</span>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li><span class="label-driver">風險原因：</span> {{ w.reason }}</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
{% endfor %}

<h3>四、週度潛力觀察名單</h3>
{% for w in ai_analysis.watchlist %}
  <div class="watch-block">
    <div>
      <span class="watch-title">{{ w.stock_id }} {{ w.name }}</span>
      <span class="watch-flag">週度潛力觀察</span>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li><span class="label-driver">推薦邏輯：</span> {{ w.reason }}</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
{% endfor %}

<h3>五、下週整體風險提醒</h3>
<blockquote>{{ ai_analysis.overall_risk }}</blockquote>
{% endif %}

<div class="footer">
  本週報由 AI 自動產生，僅供參考，不構成投資建議。週度 scoring 屬探索性質、未經 IC 驗證。
</div>

</body>
</html>
